== 評價 ==
這部電影廣受好評。<ref>{{cite web|title=Oh My God Reviews|url=http://www.indicine.com/bollywood/oh-my-god/reviews/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102161650/http://www.indicine.com/bollywood/oh-my-god/reviews/|archive-date=2013-11-02|publisher=Indicine|access-date=1 October 2012|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

{{link-en|Bollywood Hungama}}的{{link-en|塔蘭·阿達什|Taran Adarsh}}給這部電影3.5顆星（滿分5顆星）的評價，並說：“總體而言，'''偶滴神啊'''是一部非常成功的戲劇的發人深省的改編。一部處理敏感和未觸及的主題的電影，它會發現自己的支持者和對手的份額，但電影傳達的社會資訊是響亮和明確的，這就是'''偶滴神啊'''為值得觀看的主要原因之一。”<ref>{{cite web|last=Adarsh|first=Taran|title=Taran Adarsh review|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/criticreview/id/549384|publisher={{link-en|Bollywood Hungama|Bollywood Hungama}}|date=27 September 2012|access-date=27 September 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103104957/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/criticreview/id/549384|archive-date=2013-11-03|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[雷迪夫網|雷迪夫網]]的蘇卡尼亞·韋爾馬（Sukanya Verma）將其評為“滿分5分”中的4分，其中“諷刺，寓言和幻想的勇敢而令人著迷，使我們關注宗教的濫用和商業化。”<ref>{{cite web|last=Verma|first=Sukanya|title=Review: OMG – Oh My God is brave and absorbing|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/review-oh-my-god-is-a-brave-absorbing-take-on-religion/20120928.htm|work=[[雷迪夫網|雷迪夫網]]|date=28 September 2012|access-date=28 September 2012|archive-date=2012-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120930040448/http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/review-oh-my-god-is-a-brave-absorbing-take-on-religion/20120928.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 獨立寶萊塢（Independent Bollywood）的{{link-en|費薩爾·賽義夫|Faisal Saif}}將其評為5分中的4分，並說：“強烈推薦。無畏理念與一些無厘頭的表演。”<ref>{{cite news|last=Saif|first=Faisal|access-date=29 September 2012|title=OMG: Oh My God|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/movie-review/OMG-Oh-My-God/movie-review/16545873.cms|newspaper=The Times of India|archive-date=2013-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101050223/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/movie-review/OMG-Oh-My-God/movie-review/16545873.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

